high_descs: Turn around and walk until you are even with the coffee table on your left and then turn left to face it.
Pick up the credit card that's in front of you.
Turn around to face the laptop and shift ever so slightly to your right.
Set the credit card on the edge of the couch to the right of the laptop.
Walk around to the other side of the coffee table so it's between you and the couch.
Pick up the other credit card that's in front of you.
Walk back to where you put the first credit card.
Set the credit card about half a foot to the right of the first credit card and line them up so they are both going the same direction.

Pick up the credit card on the table.
Walk around the table and back to the couch.
Place the credit card to the right of the other card and in front of the pillow.
